name: 1,2,3,4-tetrahydronaphthalene-2,6-dicarboxylic acid, dimethyl ester
Restrictions: Only to be used as a co-monomer in the manufacture of a polyester non-food contact layer in a plastic multilayer material, which is to be used only in contact with foods for which food simulants A, B, C and/or D1 are assigned in Table 2 of Annex III.The specific migration limit in column 8 refers to the sum of the substance and of its dimers (cyclic and open chain).
ExpressedAs: As the sum of the substance and of its dimers (cyclic and open chain)
